[SPEAKER_01] može sve.

2352
01:28:21,939 --> 01:28:23,439
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da,

2353
01:28:23,439 --> 01:28:25,319
[SPEAKER_01] da to je to.

2354
01:28:25,319 --> 01:28:26,340
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da život u Americi

2355
01:28:26,340 --> 01:28:27,420
[SPEAKER_01] je definitivno težak.

2356
01:28:27,420 --> 01:28:28,960
[SPEAKER_01] I financijski.

2357
01:28:28,960 --> 01:28:30,819
[SPEAKER_00] A vrijednostno,

2358
01:28:30,819 --> 01:28:32,279
[SPEAKER_00] ono kao u smislu

2359
01:28:32,279 --> 01:28:34,979
[SPEAKER_00] onoga što je tebi bilo vrijedno,

2360
01:28:34,979 --> 01:28:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] pa dolaziš u nekakav drugačiji sustav,

2361
01:28:37,039 --> 01:28:38,659
[SPEAKER_00] radiš s ljudima

2362
01:28:38,659 --> 01:28:40,439
[SPEAKER_00] koji drugačije razmišljaju.

2363
01:28:41,920 --> 01:28:43,300
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko ti je to bilo izazovno?

2364
01:28:43,300 --> 01:28:45,439
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nije.

2365
01:28:45,439 --> 01:28:45,859
[SPEAKER_00] Nije?

2366
01:28:45,859 --> 01:28:50,399
[SPEAKER_01] Ne bih rekao da je nešto sad to bilo izazovno.

2367
01:28:50,399 --> 01:28:52,779
[SPEAKER_01] I sad nekako uvijek sam otvoren bio.

2368
01:28:52,779 --> 01:28:53,899
[SPEAKER_01] Bio sam otvoren ima staru,

2369
01:28:53,899 --> 01:28:54,939
[SPEAKER_01] po mi nije nešto sad bilo.

2370
01:28:56,380 --> 01:28:58,039
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, wow, što ovo znači?

2371
01:28:58,039 --> 01:28:59,979
[SPEAKER_01] Kao, kako se ovako pristupa?

2372
01:28:59,979 --> 01:29:01,520
[SPEAKER_01] Samo što kod njih

2373
01:29:01,520 --> 01:29:06,159
[SPEAKER_01] nemaju vremena

2374
01:29:06,159 --> 01:29:10,319
[SPEAKER_01] za tvoju neku bojku, recimo.

2375
01:29:10,319 --> 01:29:12,680
[SPEAKER_01] Kao nešto, kao fazon,

2376
01:29:12,680 --> 01:29:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] recimo, sad se ti razbališ.

2377
01:29:14,000 --> 01:29:14,460
[SPEAKER_00] Aha.

2378
01:29:14,460 --> 01:29:16,260
[SPEAKER_01] Nema on vremena za to.

2379
01:29:16,260 --> 01:29:17,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ne može, recimo,

2380
01:29:17,420 --> 01:29:19,300
[SPEAKER_01] odmah ti men kaže

2381
01:29:19,300 --> 01:29:20,659
[SPEAKER_01] da ja mogu računati na tebe

2382
01:29:20,659 --> 01:29:21,899
[SPEAKER_01] i da ja tebe stavim tu.

2383
01:29:23,579 --> 01:29:24,659
[SPEAKER_00] I eto ti pritiska,

2384
01:29:24,659 --> 01:29:25,819
[SPEAKER_00] ne smiješ se razlostiti.

2385
01:29:25,819 --> 01:29:26,640
[SPEAKER_00] Bolestan je ovo.

2386
01:29:26,640 --> 01:29:28,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ajde ti, ide, riječ se,

2387
01:29:28,500 --> 01:29:29,680
[SPEAKER_01] ja ću na god u ovu načinu.

2388
01:29:29,680 --> 01:29:31,039
[SPEAKER_01] Samo tako su.

2389
01:29:31,039 --> 01:29:31,859
[SPEAKER_01] On, mislim,

2390
01:29:31,859 --> 01:29:33,380
[SPEAKER_01] toksično rade.

2391
01:29:33,380 --> 01:29:34,560
[SPEAKER_01] U smislu, baš,

2392
01:29:34,560 --> 01:29:37,260
[SPEAKER_01] nije u redu ono liko raditi.

2393
01:29:37,260 --> 01:29:38,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo sad stvarno zvuče,

2394
01:29:38,760 --> 01:29:40,060
[SPEAKER_01] ono kao, ja, ima njega ljeguza.

2395
01:29:40,060 --> 01:29:40,579
[SPEAKER_01] Nije ljeguza,

2396
01:29:40,579 --> 01:29:41,500
[SPEAKER_01] nego, brate, nije u redu.

2397
01:29:41,500 --> 01:29:42,600
[SPEAKER_01] Nije u redu.

2398
01:29:42,600 --> 01:29:43,119
[SPEAKER_01] Nije u redu, nemaš ljudskost.

2399
01:29:43,119 --> 01:29:44,079
[SPEAKER_01] Gubiš ljudskost,

2400
01:29:44,079 --> 01:29:45,779
[SPEAKER_01] gubiš pristup ljudima,

2401
01:29:45,779 --> 01:29:46,380
[SPEAKER_01] gubiš,

2402
01:29:46,920 --> 01:29:48,220
[SPEAKER_01] kako se priča s ljudima,

2403
01:29:48,220 --> 01:29:48,680
[SPEAKER_01] mislim,

2404
01:29:48,680 --> 01:29:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] evo,

2405
01:29:49,000 --> 01:29:50,119
[SPEAKER_01] taj rush hour,

2406
01:29:50,119 --> 01:29:51,239
[SPEAKER_01] njihovo u osam ujitru,

2407
01:29:51,239 --> 01:29:52,739
[SPEAKER_01] kad svi idu na posao.

2408
01:29:52,739 --> 01:29:54,960
[SPEAKER_01] Združen, mislim,

2409
01:29:54,960 --> 01:29:56,020
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo bili kod sardine,

2410
01:29:56,020 --> 01:29:57,100
[SPEAKER_01] u onom vozu.

2411
01:29:57,100 --> 01:29:58,960
[SPEAKER_01] Svi jedno na drugom,

2412
01:29:58,960 --> 01:29:59,399
[SPEAKER_01] ovako,

2413
01:29:59,399 --> 01:30:00,979
[SPEAKER_01] niko si šute,

2414
01:30:00,979 --> 01:30:01,979
[SPEAKER_01] ne mogu gledati nikoga,

2415
01:30:01,979 --> 01:30:03,260
[SPEAKER_01] sam svoj posao.

2416
01:30:03,260 --> 01:30:04,439
[SPEAKER_01] da uđe neko koji je,

2417
01:30:04,439 --> 01:30:04,779
[SPEAKER_01] recimo,

2418
01:30:04,779 --> 01:30:06,140
[SPEAKER_01] beskućnik

2419
01:30:06,140 --> 01:30:09,100
[SPEAKER_01] i vjerovatno,

2420
01:30:09,100 --> 01:30:09,939
[SPEAKER_01] možda nije vjerovatno,

2421
01:30:09,939 --> 01:30:11,739
[SPEAKER_01] go mentalno,

2422
01:30:11,739 --> 01:30:14,659
[SPEAKER_01] mentalno izazvana osoba,

2423
01:30:14,659 --> 01:30:17,420
[SPEAKER_01] brišti,

2424
01:30:17,420 --> 01:30:18,239
[SPEAKER_01] darese,

2425
01:30:18,239 --> 01:30:19,380
[SPEAKER_01] baca,

2426
01:30:19,380 --> 01:30:20,180
[SPEAKER_01] razbacuje.

2427
01:30:20,180 --> 01:30:21,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ti, kao trebaš na posao.

2428
01:30:21,659 --> 01:30:24,180
[SPEAKER_00] Ali s vremenom,

2429
01:30:24,180 --> 01:30:24,800
[SPEAKER_00] pretpostavljam,

2430
01:30:24,800 --> 01:30:26,739
[SPEAKER_00] i da otupiš koliko toga vidiš.

2431
01:30:26,739 --> 01:30:27,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ti izvađeš,

2432
01:30:27,420 --> 01:30:27,920
[SPEAKER_01] sprejte me,

2433
01:30:27,920 --> 01:30:29,380
[SPEAKER_01] jedno četiri beskućnika,

2434
01:30:29,380 --> 01:30:30,180
[SPEAKER_01] tražete,

2435
01:30:30,180 --> 01:30:31,659
[SPEAKER_01] čupajte na što te traže.

2436
01:30:32,359 --> 01:30:33,619
[SPEAKER_01] ti, ono, skrećeš,

2437
01:30:33,619 --> 01:30:34,300
[SPEAKER_01] ideš dalje,

2438
01:30:34,300 --> 01:30:35,260
[SPEAKER_01] prelaziš,

2439
01:30:35,260 --> 01:30:35,659
[SPEAKER_01] često,

2440
01:30:35,659 --> 01:30:36,220
[SPEAKER_01] bibiću,

2441
01:30:36,220 --> 01:30:36,739
[SPEAKER_01] auta.

2442
01:30:36,739 --> 01:30:38,399
[SPEAKER_00] Kod nas kažu da sve šta ne valja,

2443
01:30:38,399 --> 01:30:39,340
[SPEAKER_00] došlo iz Amerike,

2444
01:30:39,340 --> 01:30:40,539
[SPEAKER_00] taj konzumerizam,

2445
01:30:40,539 --> 01:30:41,140
[SPEAKER_00] ta trka,

2446
01:30:41,140 --> 01:30:42,399
[SPEAKER_00] tako radno vrijeme.

2447
01:30:42,399 --> 01:30:42,920
[SPEAKER_00] Taj konzumerizam mu upropastio.

2448
01:30:42,920 --> 01:30:44,840
[SPEAKER_01] Njih je konzumerizam upropastio

2449
01:30:44,840 --> 01:30:46,479
[SPEAKER_01] i konzumerizam će biti njihov kraj.

2450
01:30:46,479 --> 01:30:48,020
[SPEAKER_01] On će na kraju sami sebe pojesti.

2451
01:30:48,020 --> 01:30:49,979
[SPEAKER_01] Od konzumerizma.

2452
01:30:49,979 --> 01:30:53,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ja mislim da će Amerika

2453
01:30:53,340 --> 01:30:54,220
[SPEAKER_01] sama sebe probutati

2454
01:30:54,220 --> 01:30:55,300
[SPEAKER_01] zbog to konzumerizma

2455
01:30:55,300 --> 01:30:56,619
[SPEAKER_01] i daj, daj, gravi, gravi.

2456
01:30:56,619 --> 01:30:57,460
[SPEAKER_01] Inače,

2457
01:30:57,560 --> 01:31:00,119
[SPEAKER_01] pohlepno sama sebe pojede

2458
01:31:00,119 --> 01:31:00,539
[SPEAKER_01] na kraju.

2459
01:31:00,539 --> 01:31:01,340
[SPEAKER_01] To je činičnost.

2460
01:31:01,340 --> 01:31:03,560
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ti budi pohlepno.

2461
01:31:03,560 --> 01:31:03,800
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

2462
01:31:03,800 --> 01:31:05,720
[SPEAKER_01] Pa onda vadi i jedi.

2463
01:31:06,800 --> 01:31:09,260
[SPEAKER_00] Pa je tako da...

2464
01:31:09,260 --> 01:31:11,420
[SPEAKER_00] Vidiš li se kao da bi mogao živjeti

2465
01:31:11,420 --> 01:31:13,020
[SPEAKER_00] ono do kraja života tamo?

2466
01:31:13,020 --> 01:31:15,239
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne, ne.

2467
01:31:15,239 --> 01:31:16,380
[SPEAKER_00] A planiraš se vraćati?

2468
01:31:16,380 --> 01:31:18,460
[SPEAKER_01] Pa da, mislim još nešto nekog rada.

2469
01:31:18,460 --> 01:31:20,319
[SPEAKER_01] Imam nekih planova još u New Yorku

2470
01:31:20,319 --> 01:31:21,560
[SPEAKER_01] da završim neke projekte

2471
01:31:21,560 --> 01:31:23,260
[SPEAKER_01] koje hoću da završim, odradim.

2472
01:31:23,260 --> 01:31:26,819
[SPEAKER_01] Ali živjeti tamo, mislim, u New Yorku,

2473
01:31:26,819 --> 01:31:27,659
[SPEAKER_01] kad neko kaže

2474
01:31:27,659 --> 01:31:29,060
[SPEAKER_01] ja hoću da živim u New Yorku,

2475
01:31:29,060 --> 01:31:31,720
[SPEAKER_01] obitelj, ja mislim da malo tu nešto nimaš.

2476
01:31:32,319 --> 01:31:34,020
[SPEAKER_00] Možda da ne znaš šta ga čeka.

2477
01:31:34,020 --> 01:31:35,840
[SPEAKER_00] Premjer je kao da ne znaš šta ga čeka,

2478
01:31:35,840 --> 01:31:37,119
[SPEAKER_00] samo mislim da nisu dobro,

2479
01:31:37,119 --> 01:31:38,960
[SPEAKER_01] nije zbirka,

2480
01:31:38,960 --> 01:31:40,760
[SPEAKER_01] nije zbroj dobar.

2481
01:31:40,760 --> 01:31:43,279
[SPEAKER_01] Da bi će New Yorkan reći.

2482
01:31:43,279 --> 01:31:46,439
[SPEAKER_01] Ne moj živjeti ovdje, obitelj, sada.

2483
01:31:46,439 --> 01:31:47,760
[SPEAKER_01] Drugo je da ti dođeš da rad,

2484
01:31:47,760 --> 01:31:49,619
[SPEAKER_01] New York je grad u kojoj ti dođeš da radiš.

2485
01:31:49,619 --> 01:31:52,640
[SPEAKER_01] Dođeš na 5-6 godina da radiš,

2486
01:31:52,640 --> 01:31:54,039
[SPEAKER_01] eventualno desetak,

2487
01:31:54,039 --> 01:31:57,140
[SPEAKER_01] ono, izgoriš, pregoriš

2488
01:31:57,140 --> 01:32:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] i onda se smiriš.

2489
01:32:00,000 --> 01:32:02,300
[SPEAKER_01] Idealni kad si jako,

2490
01:32:02,319 --> 01:32:02,819
[SPEAKER_01] mlad,

2491
01:32:02,819 --> 01:32:05,500
[SPEAKER_01] pa ti sva ta žiža,

2492
01:32:05,500 --> 01:32:07,739
[SPEAKER_01] ludi, loši, izogovara,

2493
01:32:07,739 --> 01:32:10,159
[SPEAKER_01] pa te tad lako nekako

2494
01:32:10,159 --> 01:32:10,880
[SPEAKER_01] i omađija,

2495
01:32:10,880 --> 01:32:13,760
[SPEAKER_01] ali ja sam došao sa 25 godina tamo.

2496
01:32:13,760 --> 01:32:16,220
[SPEAKER_01] A već drugi imao sistem,

2497
01:32:16,220 --> 01:32:18,220
[SPEAKER_01] već i drugi neki razvoj.

2498
01:32:18,220 --> 01:32:23,739
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da ne planiram

2499
01:32:23,739 --> 01:32:26,020
[SPEAKER_01] živjeti u New Yorku.

2500
01:32:26,020 --> 01:32:27,420
[SPEAKER_01] Da li planiram živjeti u Amerisku,

2501
01:32:27,420 --> 01:32:28,420
[SPEAKER_01] kada svog života?

2502
01:32:28,420 --> 01:32:31,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ne.

2503
01:32:32,140 --> 01:32:33,039
[SPEAKER_01] nemoj povijem.

2504
01:32:33,039 --> 01:32:34,979
[SPEAKER_01] Što moga pituje?

2505
01:32:34,979 --> 01:32:35,380
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim što će.

2506
01:32:35,380 --> 01:32:38,439
[SPEAKER_01] Planiranje često demantujem svim

2507
01:32:38,439 --> 01:32:39,840
[SPEAKER_01] hodima na medijima je to.

2508
01:32:39,840 --> 01:32:40,760
[SPEAKER_01] Kako planiranje?

2509
01:32:40,760 --> 01:32:41,539
[SPEAKER_01] Šta planiramo?

2510
01:32:41,539 --> 01:32:43,579
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, kada se nešto je ovaj

2511
01:32:43,579 --> 01:32:45,260
[SPEAKER_01] COVID naučio da ne planiramo.

2512
01:32:45,260 --> 01:32:46,399
[SPEAKER_01] Nema smisla.

2513
01:32:46,399 --> 01:32:47,520
[SPEAKER_01] Mogu ja sad nešto

2514
01:32:47,520 --> 01:32:48,079
[SPEAKER_01] koje ima cilj.

2515
01:32:48,079 --> 01:32:48,760
[SPEAKER_01] To je druga stav.

2516
01:32:48,760 --> 01:32:49,159
[SPEAKER_01] To je super.

2517
01:32:49,619 --> 01:32:50,340
[SPEAKER_01] ima ti cilj.

2518
01:32:50,340 --> 01:32:51,039
[SPEAKER_01] Zapiš ti sebe

2519
01:32:51,039 --> 01:32:51,899
[SPEAKER_01] mart 13.

2520
01:32:51,899 --> 01:32:55,279
[SPEAKER_01] Dotađa to rad.

2521
01:32:55,279 --> 01:32:55,600
[SPEAKER_01] Bravo.

2522
01:32:55,600 --> 01:32:58,479
[SPEAKER_01] I samo stavi taj datum.

2523
01:32:58,479 --> 01:32:59,100
[SPEAKER_01] To je okej.

2524
01:32:59,619 --> 01:33:02,920
[SPEAKER_01] A sad ti da se planiraš svaki dan, svaki sad, družaj.

2525
01:33:02,920 --> 01:33:04,380
[SPEAKER_01] Nije se to u redu.

2526
01:33:04,380 --> 01:33:06,800
[SPEAKER_00] Uvijek uzmi u obzir da se neće ustaviti.

2527
01:33:06,800 --> 01:33:08,680
[SPEAKER_01] Treba se naći neki balans, jel?

2528
01:33:08,680 --> 01:33:11,979
[SPEAKER_01] I planirat, ali ne ostaviti fleksibilnosti.

2529
01:33:11,979 --> 01:33:12,840
[SPEAKER_01] I spontanost.

2530
01:33:12,840 --> 01:33:13,319
[SPEAKER_01] E, to.

2531
01:33:13,319 --> 01:33:15,079
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš, mislim, opet ode život.

2532
01:33:15,079 --> 01:33:18,739
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš, malo da si spontan, malo da si avanturističan,

2533
01:33:18,739 --> 01:33:20,180
[SPEAKER_01] malo da čuješ nekoga.

2534
01:33:20,180 --> 01:33:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ti čim ti sve isplaniraš, ti ne možeš ne čuti ljudi.

2535
01:33:23,000 --> 01:33:25,319
[SPEAKER_01] Ti znaš što tebe neko treba pitat,

2536
01:33:25,319 --> 01:33:28,319
[SPEAKER_01] pod kojim okolostima i te stvari.

2537
01:33:28,319 --> 01:33:29,100
[SPEAKER_01] To stvara se isti...

2538
01:33:29,100 --> 01:33:31,680
[SPEAKER_00] I ti planovi idu nekako uz onom priču o kalupima,

2539
01:33:31,680 --> 01:33:35,180
[SPEAKER_00] o kvirima, u kojima nas odgajaju juče,

2540
01:33:35,279 --> 01:33:38,340
[SPEAKER_00] a ti si neko ko je odlučio izaći iz kalupa.

2541
01:33:38,340 --> 01:33:39,539
[SPEAKER_00] Što bi...

2542
01:33:39,539 --> 01:33:41,420
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, sad ono, pitanje za kraj.

2543
01:33:41,420 --> 01:33:44,680
[SPEAKER_00] Malo će biti drugačije nego u onom dijelu razgovora.

2544
01:33:44,680 --> 01:33:46,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, evo, što bi sad ti,

2545
01:33:46,779 --> 01:33:50,260
[SPEAKER_00] kao odrasla osoba ostvarena,

2546
01:33:50,260 --> 01:33:52,720
[SPEAKER_00] rekao nekom malom goranu

2547
01:33:52,720 --> 01:33:55,699
[SPEAKER_00] koji je počeo lagano iskakati iz kalupa?

2548
01:33:55,699 --> 01:33:57,260
[SPEAKER_01] Ma bravo, Udrijače.

2549
01:33:57,260 --> 01:33:59,239
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro reko.

2550
01:33:59,239 --> 01:34:01,300
[SPEAKER_01] Ma bravo, Udrijače.

2551
01:34:01,300 --> 01:34:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to mislim da je točno ono što sam,

2552
01:34:05,279 --> 01:34:10,100
[SPEAKER_01] kao djete učinio i što sam radio i kako sam, ono, šizika.

2553
01:34:10,100 --> 01:34:15,319
[SPEAKER_01] Bio mislim da je to upravo ono što sam ja trebao da ugradim.

