2733
01:42:59,060 --> 01:43:01,840
[SPEAKER_01] Iako si mirote, ja sam remek dijelo, ono, gore.

2734
01:43:01,840 --> 01:43:03,359
[SPEAKER_01] Ne tvoje.

2735
01:43:03,359 --> 01:43:06,319
[SPEAKER_00] Bravo, Goran.

2736
01:43:06,319 --> 01:43:07,260
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da.

2737
01:43:07,340 --> 01:43:09,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ti si mi poduška, krila.

2738
01:43:09,840 --> 01:43:11,500
[SPEAKER_01] Rote su krila djece.

2739
01:43:11,500 --> 01:43:12,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bih nekao.

2740
01:43:12,619 --> 01:43:13,380
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

2741
01:43:13,380 --> 01:43:14,579
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je, to je tvoje.

2742
01:43:14,579 --> 01:43:18,220
[SPEAKER_00] Da, a i djeci ne bi trebali rezati njihova krila.

2743
01:43:18,220 --> 01:43:19,560
[SPEAKER_01] Ni slučajno, ni slučajno.

2744
01:43:19,560 --> 01:43:22,960
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala ti puno, baš je ugodno s tobom razgovarati.

2745
01:43:23,300 --> 01:43:26,159
[SPEAKER_01] Također, također, baš mi je bilo super ovo.

2746
01:43:26,159 --> 01:43:27,180
[SPEAKER_00] Baš mi je drago.

2747
01:43:27,180 --> 01:43:37,340
[SPEAKER_00] Želim ti svu sreću i baš se veselim svim novim isječicima koje ćeš nam priuštiti u svim likovima.

2748
01:43:37,939 --> 01:43:44,100
[SPEAKER_00] I, evo to, hvala ti što radiš ovaj po sobo ljudni, da se opet pratim na to.

2749
01:43:44,100 --> 01:43:46,439
[SPEAKER_00] Balkan majka liječi traume.

2750
01:43:46,439 --> 01:43:48,819
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu hvala.

2751
01:43:48,819 --> 01:43:52,819
[SPEAKER_00] Samo ko je dovoljno svjestan da to prepozna.

2752
01:43:52,819 --> 01:43:53,800
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

2753
01:43:53,800 --> 01:43:55,500
[SPEAKER_00] I, eto, nastavi dalje.

2754
01:43:55,500 --> 01:43:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

2755
01:43:56,000 --> 01:43:57,779
[SPEAKER_01] Percepcija traume je drugačija.

2756
01:43:57,779 --> 01:44:00,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ću tebi opet sada ovo tvoje parapraz...

2757
01:44:00,260 --> 01:44:02,239
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, ponoviću ti udrijače.

2758
01:44:02,239 --> 01:44:02,500
[SPEAKER_00] Udrijače.

2759
01:44:02,500 --> 01:44:03,300
[SPEAKER_01] Samo nastavi.

2760
01:44:03,300 --> 01:44:05,720
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno. Hvala puno na pozivu.

2761
01:44:05,720 --> 01:44:07,520
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo mi je jako ugodno razgovarati s tobom.

2762
01:44:07,520 --> 01:44:10,319
[SPEAKER_01] Pozdrav gledateljima i slušteljima podcasta.

2763
01:44:10,319 --> 01:44:11,720
[SPEAKER_01] Rastuću i sad.

2764
01:44:11,720 --> 01:44:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde ti im reci da se pretplati da ja ne moram.

2765
01:44:14,000 --> 01:44:14,779
[SPEAKER_01] Aha.

2766
01:44:14,779 --> 01:44:16,180
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš šta?

2767
01:44:17,880 --> 01:44:19,119
[SPEAKER_00] Šta to znaš?

2768
01:44:19,119 --> 01:44:19,600
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš šta?

2769
01:44:19,600 --> 01:44:22,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ima da se pretplatiš.

2770
01:44:22,739 --> 01:44:24,500
[SPEAKER_01] Čuj.

2771
01:44:24,500 --> 01:44:25,699
[SPEAKER_01] No ti ja dolazim.

2772
01:44:25,699 --> 01:44:27,260
[SPEAKER_01] Gledam te.

2773
01:44:27,260 --> 01:44:27,899
[SPEAKER_01] Vidim te.

2774
01:44:27,899 --> 01:44:29,239
[SPEAKER_01] Kroz kameru.

2775
01:44:29,239 --> 01:44:30,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ajme dalje.

2776
01:44:30,199 --> 01:44:30,960
[SPEAKER_01] Pretplaci se.

2777
01:44:30,960 --> 01:44:32,579
[SPEAKER_01] Nemoj molite da te ja sad pronalazim.

2778
01:44:32,579 --> 01:44:35,020
[SPEAKER_01] Ako vas nađem da se niste pretplatili,

2779
01:44:35,020 --> 01:44:37,180
[SPEAKER_01] sve ću vas otpratiti.

2780
01:44:37,180 --> 01:44:40,079
[SPEAKER_01] Sali, samo pretplate se.

2781
01:44:40,079 --> 01:44:40,560
[SPEAKER_01] Što da ne?

2782
01:44:40,560 --> 01:44:40,880
[SPEAKER_01] Šta?

2783
01:44:40,880 --> 01:44:41,779
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa vas ne košta.

2784
01:44:41,779 --> 01:44:42,500
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

2785
01:44:42,500 --> 01:44:43,039
[SPEAKER_01] Eto to je to.

2786
01:44:43,039 --> 01:44:43,579
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ja, samo se pretplatite.

2787
01:44:43,579 --> 01:44:45,439
[SPEAKER_00] Samo se tako zove pretplatite.

2788
01:44:45,439 --> 01:44:46,899
[SPEAKER_01] Joj, strašno.

2789
01:44:46,939 --> 01:44:48,619
[SPEAKER_01] Postan te stjedbenik.

2790
01:44:48,619 --> 01:44:50,239
[SPEAKER_01] Na Ubitul.

2791
01:44:50,239 --> 01:44:52,920
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala ti, Gora.

2792
01:44:52,920 --> 01:44:55,060
[SPEAKER_01] Šta ja radim, osebe sa svoje 32 godine.

2793
01:44:55,060 --> 01:44:55,899
[SPEAKER_01] Čujemo se kasnije.

2794
01:44:55,899 --> 01:44:57,460
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala ti.

2795
01:44:57,460 --> 01:44:58,460
[SPEAKER_00] Pratiti ćemo te.

2796
01:44:58,460 --> 01:45:00,859
[SPEAKER_00] Pratite i podcast Rastući s djecom.

2797
01:45:00,859 --> 01:45:04,220
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala Hipu koji nas prati, podržava.

2798
01:45:04,220 --> 01:45:07,239
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa, nova epizoda stiže za dva tjedna.

